	<article>
		<h2 class="heading" id="categories">Managing Categories and Subcategories</h2>
		<div class="content">
			<p>Categories are simple to create.  <b>You'll probably want to do so before you create any products.</b> Click on "Categories" in the main menu at the top of the page, and click "New Category" at the bottom of the screen.  Just enter a name and click "Create."</p> 
			<p>Then, you can add subcategories to each category. <b>You MUST create a subcategory for each category or the products you assign to them will not be visible in the front store.</b><i>If a category doesn't have a subcategory, just add a subcategory named "All."</i></p> 
			<p> You cannot delete categories but you can remove subcategories.  Both are editable.</p>
		</div>
	</article>
	
