		<div class="content">
			<p>To manage the images that fade in and out on the front page click on "Front Sliders" in the navigation menu.  Click "New Slider," enter a name, and upload a picture.  You'll be taken to a screen where you can crop the image to the correct dimensions.</p>
			<p>On the main slider page, you can edit (re-upload) or delete a slider.</p>
		</div>
