		<h2 class="heading" id="front">Managing Other Front Page Options</h2>
		<div class="content">
			<p>There are a few other options you can set on the front page.</p>
			<b>Featured Product</b>
			<p>You can feature one of your products on the front page: click on "Front Options" in the main navigation bar.  There you can select one of your products to feature.  The image and description will automatically appear on the front page.</p>
			
			<b>Catalogue/Other Feature</b>
			<p>You also have the flexibility of uploading another feature for the front page.  This can be anything you like.  Under "Catalogue Feature" upload a picture and enter a heading and description.  You'll be able to crop the image afterwards.</p>
		</div>
